org.sakaiproject.assignment.api

Interface AssignmentSubmission

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Entity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AssignmentSubmissionEdit
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseAssignmentService.BaseAssignmentSubmission, BaseAssignmentService.BaseAssignmentSubmissionEdit

    public interface AssignmentSubmission
extends Entity

    AssignmentSubmission is the an interface for the Sakai assignments module. It represents student submissions for assignments.
